## Design Decisions

| Feature | Implementation | Why? |
|---------|----------------|------|
| `rounded-full` buttons | Pill shape for all interactive elements | Creates soft, luxury feel per design system |
| `backdrop-blur-md` on header | Semi-transparent sticky header | Modern, premium aesthetic while maintaining readability |
| Spring animations | `stiffness: 400, damping: 40` | Natural-feeling motion that doesn't feel sluggish |
| 150ms hover delay | Timeout before closing mega menu | Prevents accidental closure when moving cursor |
| Body scroll lock | When mobile drawer is open | Standard UX pattern for modal overlays |

